						               													<description>Say goodbye to Earth. The race is on to colonize Venus.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Inspired on the one hit wonder song The Final Countdown by Europe.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;In our third month of one hit wonders, we have a game inspired by The Final Countdown, which 100% makes me think of Gob Bluth from Arrested Development. In this game, you will try to get all cards from 10-A then claim &amp;quot;It's the final countdown!&amp;quot; to win. There's a little press your luck, and some fun face-card powers, as well as the ongoing tradition of great starting player rules.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the publisher&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Leaving Ground is a trick-taking game played with a regular deck of cards, in which players attempt to complete a countdown to launch their rockets by assembling a run from 10 to A (of any suit); winning a trick doesn't award all cards played, but gives a powerful bonus that can give an edge over your competition. Face cards, while not contributing to your countdown, have special abilities that can be used to affect gameplay -- perhaps just what you need to eke out a win!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the publisher&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Delivered on Board Game of the Month Club March 2017 package.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
